{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"When I heard those bars"},{"time":4360,"text":"slam hard,"},{"time":8119,"text":"I knew it was for real."},{"time":11520,"text":"I feel confused."},{"time":14480,"text":"I feel betrayed."},{"time":17880,"text":"I feel overwhelmed."},{"time":21760,"text":"I feel silenced."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25760,"text":"What just happened?"},{"time":28680,"text":"How could they send me here?"},{"time":32040,"text":"I don't belong here."},{"time":35360,"text":"How could they make such a huge mistake"},{"time":39280,"text":"without any repercussions\nwhatsoever to their actions?"},{"time":45080,"text":"I see large groups of women"},{"time":48520,"text":"in tattered uniforms"},{"time":50880,"text":"surrounded by huge walls and gates,"},{"time":55440,"text":"enclosed by iron barbed wires,"},{"time":58760,"text":"and I get hit by an awful stench,"},{"time":62880,"text":"and I ask myself,"},{"time":65519,"text":"how did I move"},{"time":68320,"text":"from working in the respected\nfinancial banking sector,"},{"time":74120,"text":"having worked so hard in school,"},{"time":78000,"text":"to now being locked up"},{"time":80600,"text":"in the largest correctional facility"},{"time":83840,"text":"for women in Kenya?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87520,"text":"My first night"},{"time":89680,"text":"at Langata Women Maximum Security Prison"},{"time":93840,"text":"was the toughest."},{"time":96400,"text":"In January of 2009,"},{"time":99480,"text":"I was informed that I had handled\na fraudulent transaction unknowingly"},{"time":104160,"text":"at the bank where I worked."},{"time":106680,"text":"I was shocked, scared and terrified."},{"time":111320,"text":"I would lose a career\nthat I loved passionately."},{"time":117320,"text":"But that was not the worst."},{"time":120400,"text":"It got even worse\nthan I could have ever imagined."},{"time":125920,"text":"I got arrested,"},{"time":128440,"text":"maliciously charged"},{"time":130600,"text":"and prosecuted."},{"time":134440,"text":"The absurdity of it all\nwas the arresting officer"},{"time":139040,"text":"asking me to pay him 10,000 US dollars"},{"time":144200,"text":"and the case would disappear."},{"time":147840,"text":"I refused."},{"time":150560,"text":"Two and a half years on,"},{"time":153320,"text":"in and out of courts,"},{"time":155080,"text":"fighting to prove my innocence."},{"time":158560,"text":"It was all over the media,"},{"time":161560,"text":"in the newspapers, TV, radio."},{"time":165720,"text":"They came to me again."},{"time":168120,"text":"This time around, said to me,"},{"time":171600,"text":"\"If you give us 50,000 US dollars,"},{"time":177080,"text":"the judgement will be in your favor,\""},{"time":181480,"text":"irrespective of the fact\nthat there was no evidence whatsoever"},{"time":186480,"text":"that I had any wrongdoing"},{"time":188720,"text":"on the charges that I was up against."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193280,"text":"I remember the events"},{"time":195760,"text":"of my conviction"},{"time":197640,"text":"six years ago"},{"time":200240,"text":"as if it were yesterday."},{"time":203320,"text":"The cold, hard face of the judge"},{"time":206920,"text":"as she pronounced my sentence"},{"time":209720,"text":"on a cold Thursday morning"},{"time":213080,"text":"for a crime that I hadn't committed."},{"time":217160,"text":"I remember holding"},{"time":219160,"text":"my three-month-old beautiful daughter"},{"time":223080,"text":"whom I had just named Oma,"},{"time":226280,"text":"which in my dialect\nmeans \"truth and justice,\""},{"time":230760,"text":"as that was what I had longed so much for"},{"time":235640,"text":"all this time."},{"time":237960,"text":"I dressed her in her\nfavorite purple dress,"},{"time":241600,"text":"and here she was, about to accompany me"},{"time":245840,"text":"to serve this one-year sentence"},{"time":248600,"text":"behind bars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252280,"text":"The guards did not seem\nsensitive to the trauma"},{"time":256040,"text":"that this experience was causing me."},{"time":260440,"text":"My dignity and humanity disappeared"},{"time":265320,"text":"with the admission process."},{"time":269840,"text":"It involved me being\nsearched for contrabands,"},{"time":274680,"text":"changed from my ordinary clothes"},{"time":278000,"text":"to the prison uniform,"},{"time":279920,"text":"forced to squat on the ground,"},{"time":283800,"text":"a posture that I soon came to learn"},{"time":287080,"text":"would form the routine"},{"time":289960,"text":"of the thousands of searches,"},{"time":293200,"text":"number counts,"},{"time":294720,"text":"that lay ahead of me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"The women told me,"},{"time":301360,"text":"\"You'll adjust to this place."},{"time":304200,"text":"You'll fit right in.\""},{"time":307280,"text":"I was no longer referred to\nas Teresa Njoroge."},{"time":311360,"text":"The number 415/11 was my new identity,"},{"time":316120,"text":"and I soon learned that was\nthe case with the other women"},{"time":319960,"text":"who we were sharing this space with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324040,"text":"And adjust I did to life on the inside:"},{"time":328680,"text":"the prison food,"},{"time":331160,"text":"the prison language,"},{"time":333920,"text":"the prison life."},{"time":335920,"text":"Prison is certainly no fairytale world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342720,"text":"What I didn't see come my way"},{"time":345360,"text":"was the women and children"},{"time":349840,"text":"whom we served time and shared space with,"},{"time":355560,"text":"women who had been imprisoned"},{"time":359480,"text":"for crimes of the system,"},{"time":362560,"text":"the corruption that requires a fall guy,"},{"time":368240,"text":"a scapegoat,"},{"time":370160,"text":"so that the person who is responsible"},{"time":373040,"text":"could go free,"},{"time":375600,"text":"a broken system that routinely\nvilifies the vulnerable,"},{"time":382280,"text":"the poorest amongst us,"},{"time":384600,"text":"people who cannot afford to pay bail"},{"time":387720,"text":"or bribes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391560,"text":"And so we moved on."},{"time":394760,"text":"As I listened to story after story"},{"time":397720,"text":"of these close to 700 women"},{"time":400960,"text":"during that one year in prison,"},{"time":405360,"text":"I soon realized that crime"},{"time":409280,"text":"was not what had brought\nthese women to prison,"},{"time":414480,"text":"most of them,"},{"time":416480,"text":"far from it."},{"time":419000,"text":"It had started with the education system,"},{"time":424800,"text":"whose supply and quality\nis not equal for all;"},{"time":430280,"text":"lack of economic opportunities"},{"time":434240,"text":"that pushes these women\nto petty survival crimes;"},{"time":439120,"text":"the health system,"},{"time":441280,"text":"social justice system,"},{"time":443520,"text":"the criminal justice system."},{"time":445960,"text":"If any of these women,"},{"time":448400,"text":"who were mostly from poor backgrounds,"},{"time":451280,"text":"fall through the cracks"},{"time":454000,"text":"in the already broken system,"},{"time":457080,"text":"the bottom of that chasm is a prison,"},{"time":460880,"text":"period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464440,"text":"By the time I completed\nmy one-year sentence"},{"time":467760,"text":"at Langata Women Maximum Prison,"},{"time":471000,"text":"I had a burning conviction"},{"time":474960,"text":"to be part of the transformation"},{"time":478880,"text":"to resolve the injustices"},{"time":481440,"text":"that I had witnessed"},{"time":483160,"text":"of women and girls"},{"time":484920,"text":"who were caught up in a revolving door"},{"time":487720,"text":"of a life in and out of prison"},{"time":490280,"text":"due to poverty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493600,"text":"After my release,"},{"time":495520,"text":"I set up Clean Start."},{"time":498320,"text":"Clean Start is a social enterprise"},{"time":501840,"text":"that seeks to give these women and girls"},{"time":504840,"text":"a second chance."},{"time":507200,"text":"What we do is we build bridges for them."},{"time":510920,"text":"We go into the prisons, train them,"},{"time":513720,"text":"give them skills, tools and support"},{"time":516799,"text":"to enable them to be able\nto change their mindsets,"},{"time":520240,"text":"their behaviors and their attitudes."},{"time":523400,"text":"We also build bridges into the prisons"},{"time":527840,"text":"from the corporate sector --"},{"time":529840,"text":"individuals, organizations"},{"time":532000,"text":"that will partner with Clean Start"},{"time":534000,"text":"to enable us to provide employment,"},{"time":536440,"text":"places to call home,"},{"time":538520,"text":"jobs, vocational training,"},{"time":540680,"text":"for these women, girls,"},{"time":543000,"text":"boys and men,"},{"time":544480,"text":"upon transition back into society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548960,"text":"I never thought"},{"time":551440,"text":"that one day"},{"time":553200,"text":"I would be giving stories"},{"time":555120,"text":"of the injustices that are so common"},{"time":558680,"text":"within the criminal justice system,"},{"time":562360,"text":"but here I am."},{"time":565480,"text":"Every time I go back to prison,"},{"time":568520,"text":"I feel a little at home,"},{"time":571240,"text":"but it is the daunting work"},{"time":576120,"text":"to achieve the vision"},{"time":578080,"text":"that keeps me awake at night,"},{"time":582080,"text":"connecting the miles to Louisiana,"},{"time":586120,"text":"which is deemed as the incarceration\ncapital of the world,"},{"time":592240,"text":"carrying with me stories"},{"time":595120,"text":"of hundreds of women"},{"time":597440,"text":"whom I have met within the prisons,"},{"time":600640,"text":"some of whom are now\nembracing their second chances,"},{"time":605200,"text":"and others who are still\non that bridge of life's journey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612560,"text":"I embody a line"},{"time":615400,"text":"from the great Maya Angelou."},{"time":619040,"text":"\"I come as one,"},{"time":621600,"text":"but I stand as 10,000.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":625120,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":633640,"text":"For my story is singular,"},{"time":637120,"text":"but imagine with me"},{"time":639680,"text":"the millions of people"},{"time":643200,"text":"in prisons today,"},{"time":646280,"text":"yearning for freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651040,"text":"Three years post my conviction"},{"time":655240,"text":"and two years post my release,"},{"time":658680,"text":"I got cleared by the courts of appeal"},{"time":661680,"text":"of any wrongdoing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":668760,"text":"Around the same time,"},{"time":670840,"text":"I got blessed with my son,"},{"time":673040,"text":"whom I named Uhuru,"},{"time":675320,"text":"which in my dialect means \"freedom.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":678400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":682480,"text":"Because I had finally gotten the freedom"},{"time":686000,"text":"that I so longed for."},{"time":688720,"text":"I come as one,"},{"time":690880,"text":"but I stand as 10,000,"},{"time":693480,"text":"encouraged by the hard-edged hope"},{"time":698160,"text":"that thousands of us have come together"},{"time":701960,"text":"to reform and transform\nthe criminal justice system,"},{"time":708000,"text":"encouraged that we are doing our jobs"},{"time":712280,"text":"as we are meant to do them."},{"time":715120,"text":"And let us keep doing them"},{"time":717520,"text":"with no apology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720040,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721280,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}